<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.158104>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Scinax curicica, holotype MNRJ 26327 in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/158104/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.158105>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Scinax curicica, holotype MNRJ 26327. (A) Dorsal and (B) lateral views of head; ventral views of (C) hand and (D) foot." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/158105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169420>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Scinax curicica, adult photographed in life; Serra do Cipó, municipality of Santana do Riacho, State of Minas Gerais, Brazil; MCN 3647. Photo by B. V. S. Pimenta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169420/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.158107>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. (a) Oscillogram and (b) sonogram of Scinax curicica advertisement call; Serra do Cipó, municipality of Santana do Riacho, State of Minas Gerais, Brazil, on 0 4 July 1974. Air temperature 12 o C; water temperature 17 o C; 2100 h." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/158107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.158108>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Scinax curicica, tadpole at stage 37 (ZUEC 11835); from the type locality. (a) lateral, (b) dorsal, (c) ventral views; (d) mouth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/158108/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

